These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-1::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, train, taxi
3 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, rat
1. the owner of the rat is somewhere between the person driving the roller and the owner of the ferret##7
2. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
3. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3   |
| Transport   | taxi | train | roller |
| Pet           | ferret  | rat     | bird  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, electronic, reggae
House: farmhouse, cottage, colonial
1. the farmhouse house is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of country is somewhere between the fan of reggae and the cottage house##7
3. the farmhouse house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | country | reggae |
| House     | cottage       | colonial     | farmhouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-3::.
3 different pets are kept: snake, chinchilla, horse
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, subway, train
1. the person driving the subway is somewhere between the owner of the snake and the person driving the roller##7
2. the person driving the train is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |   3    |
| Pet    | snake | chinchilla | horse  |
| Transport   | train  | subway  | roller |

