.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  project-manager, scientist, teacher
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, subway, boat
1. the project-manager is somewhere between the person driving the boat and the scientist##7
2. the person driving the subway is not the project-manager##6
3. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the right of the person driving the subway##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |      3      |
| Job           | scientist | project-manager | teacher     |
| Transport   | subway    | roller          | boat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-5::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, rowing, surfing
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, skateboard
1. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere between the person driving the skateboard and the person who's sport is rowing##7
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Sport   | climbing      | surfing     | rowing   |
| Transport     | skateboard | quad-bike | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-6::.
3 different pets are kept: rat, mouse, hedgehog
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, japanese, pakistani
1. the colombian is on the left or right of the japanese##3
2. the japanese is somewhere to the left of the colombian##5
3. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the pakistani##1
4. the owner of the mouse is somewhere between the pakistani and the owner of the rat##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Pet   | hedgehog    | mouse     | rat     |
| Nationality   | pakistani | japanese | colombian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-7::.
3 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, rat
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, japanese, dutch
1. the dutch is on the right of the turkish##1
2. the dutch is somewhere between the owner of the goat and the turkish##7
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Pet     | rat       | goldfish      | goat       |
| Nationality   | turkish | dutch | japanese |

