.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-8::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, tram, quad-bike
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, sports, western
1. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
2. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere between the person watching western movies and the person driving the tram##7
3. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Transport           | quad-bike | snowmobile  | tram |
| Movie-Genre   | western      | mystery | sports      |

