The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, manager, teacher
1. the teacher is not the person who growsballoon-flower##6
2. the manager is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
3. the doctor is somewhere between the manager and the person who growsdaisy##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |
| Flower   | daisy | balloon-flower | azalea   |
