.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-10::.
3 different games are played: canasta, monopoly, snooker
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, skiing, tennis
1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person playing snooker is somewhere between the person playing monopoly and the person who's sport is skiing##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Game   | monopoly   | snooker    | canasta |
| Sport      | tennis | badminton | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-11::.
