There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, german, thai
1. the person playing domino is somewhere between the german and the dutch##7
2. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
3. the dutch is not the person playing bridge##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Game         | bridge | domino | backgammon |
| Nationality   | german    | thai    | dutch         |

