.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-12::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, volleyball, sailing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, superhero, zombie
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person watching superhero movies and the person who's sport is water-polo##7
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the right of the person watching scientific movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Sport          | water-polo  | sailing       | volleyball     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | scientific | superhero |

