.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-13::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, iced-tea
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, aristoff, baccarat
1. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere between the davidoff-smoker and the baccarat-smoker##7
2. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere between the davidoff-smoker and the person drinking cola##7
4. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the aristoff-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |  3   |
| Beverage      | coffee     | iced-tea | cola |
| Cigar   | davidoff | aristoff    | baccarat |

