.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-14::.
City: hannover, san-francisco, nizza
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, ship, train
1. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
2. the person driving the train is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
3. the person driving the ship is somewhere between the person driving the train and the person traveling to hannover##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| City        | san-francisco | nizza | hannover |
| Transport   | train  | ship       | bike      |

