.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-15::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, skydiving, board-games
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, swimming, water-polo
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's sport is swimming##7
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby     | board-games  | magic-tricks       | skydiving    |
| Sport   | cricket | water-polo | swimming |

