.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-16::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, peach, potato
City: boston, edinburgh, venice
1. the person eating avocado is somewhere to the right of the person eating potato##5
2. the person eating potato is the person eating potato##1
3. the person eating peach is somewhere between the person traveling to venice and the person traveling to boston##7
4. the person traveling to boston is the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | potato | peach     | avocado   |
| City   | venice   | edinburgh | boston |

