2. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking mirinda and the person who growsballoon-flower##7
3. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Beverage   | mirinda      | tea     | almond-milk |
| Flower        | marigold | azalea | balloon-flower    |

 